{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"AbstractRange.collapsed","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange/collapsed","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><em><code>collapsed</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange/endContainer\"><code>endContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange/endOffset\"><code>endOffset</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange/startContainer\"><code>startContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange/startOffset\"><code>startOffset</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code></a>의 범위가 축소된 read-only 속성은&nbsp;범위의 시작 위치와 끝 위치가 같을 경우 true를 반환합니다.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"문법","title":"문법","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>isCollpased</em> = <em>range</em>.collapsed</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>범위가 축소된 경우 true인 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a>값을 반환합니다.&nbsp; 축소된 범위는 시작 위치와 종료 위치가 동일하며, 문자 길이가 0인 범위입니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"명세","title":"명세","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"sta